<td align="center"><b>
<i>Calliopsis scitula</i> <font size="-1" face="sans-serif">Cresson, 1878</font></b><br>
<small><i>Calliopsis scitulus </i>Cresson, 1878; <i>Calliopsis pictipes </i>Cresson, 1878; <i>Spinoliella lawae </i>Michener, 1937; <i>Nomadopsis &#40;Micronomadopsis&#41; scitula scitula </i>&#40;Cresson, 1878&#41;; <i>Nomadopsis &#40;Micronomadopsis&#41; scitula lawae </i>&#40;Michener, 1937&#41;; <i>Calliopsis &#40;Micronomadopsis&#41; scitula lawae </i>&#40;Michener, 1937&#41;; <i>Calliopsis &#40;Nomadopsis&#41; scitula lawae </i>&#40;Michener, 1937&#41;, valid subspecies</small><p>
